		{"id":"0a1ffc360198b9b3","type":"text","text":"## ROOM\n- `id` `uuid` `pk`\n- `name` `varchar(50)` `unique` `not null`","x":-1180,"y":-1320,"width":400,"height":136,"color":"#069171"},
		{"id":"9aa1b615c87ee93f","type":"text","text":"## CONTAIN","x":-2376,"y":-615,"width":153,"height":62},
		{"id":"f84025695f85f577","type":"text","text":"## QUESTION\n\n- `id` `uuid` `pk`\n-  `descritpion` `varchar(50)` `not null`\n- `content` `text` `not null`\n- `upvote` `int` `default 0`\n- `email` `varchar(50)` `unique` `not null`\n- `created_at` `datetime` `default now()`\n-  `session_id` `fk` `references` session(id)\n-  `user_id` `fk` `references` user(id)\n-  `anonyme` `boolean` `default false`","x":-2499,"y":-268,"width":400,"height":328,"color":"#069171"},
		{"id":"382c0b00f25387cc","type":"text","text":"## PARTICIPATE\n\n- `id` `uuid` `not null`\n- `user_id` `fk` `not null` `references` speaker(id)\n- `session_id` `fk` `not null` `references` session(id)\n- `at` `timestamp` `default now()`  not null`","x":-643,"y":-199,"width":484,"height":220},
		{"id":"55b599f261ccf307","type":"text","text":"## INTERVENE\n\n- `id` `uuid` `not null`\n- `speaker_id` `fk` `not null` `references` user(id)\n- `session_id` `fk` `not null` `references` session(id)\n- `start_time` `time with time zone` `not null`\n- `end_time` `time with time zone` `not null`","x":-1820,"y":-199,"width":484,"height":220},
